===Etymology===
Originated 1400–50 from late {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|comparative|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|comparativus|lang=la}}, equivalent to {{term|comparatus|lang=la}}, from {{term|comparare||to compare|lang=la}} + {{term|-ive}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|-ivus|lang=la}}.

